get que je need:
dans classe player (ou dans l'interface Bomberman):
  getName()         --> name player
  getPosition()     --> position player
  getDirection()    --> direction player
  getSpeed()        --> speed player
  getTexturePath()  --> texture path
  getColor()        --> color player
    getR()          --> red intensity
    getG()          --> greed intensity
    getB()          --> blue intensity
  getScore()        --> score player
  getLeft()         --> left key
  getRight()        --> right key
  getUp()           --> up key
  getDown()         --> down key
  getBomb()         --> bomb key
  getBombs()        --> bombs vector
__________

dans classe bombe:
  getTexturePath()  --> texture path
  getTime()         --> time until explosion
  getRange()        --> range explosion
  getPosition()     --> position bomb
